Title: Lazer Gate
Description:
An assault-type arena, with two conveyor bridges, moving obstacles and a lazer gate.
The lazer gate can be turned off by pressing a button between the bridges.
Be careful! The button is surrouded by spikes & a saw blade.

Features: 4 bronze, 4 silver, 2 gold, 2 diamond, 2 titanium, 2 uranium & 2 insanium, also a lot of blue bots.

Enjoy!
